headline: Cal-Maine Foods, Inc. Names Melanie Boulden to Company’s Board of Directors
summary: RIDGELAND, Miss., August 11, 2025--Cal-Maine Foods, Inc. (NASDAQ: CALM) ("Cal-Maine Foods" or the "Company") today announced that Melanie Boulden was appointed to the Company’s Board of Directors as an independent director, effective August 11, 2025. She will serve until the 2025 Annual Meeting of Shareholders, after which she will stand for reelection as a Class I Director to serve for a three-year term.
